results.name: a(n) = n * A111089(n).
comment: Conjecture: differs from A050399 at the positions given by A089966. E.g., a(15)=75, instead of A050399(15)=225, a(30)=150, instead of A050399(30)=450, a(33)=363, instead of A050399(33)=1089, a(45)=225, instead of A050399(45)=1225. Conjecture 2: for all n > 1, a(n) divides A050399(n).
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
G. Guninski, List of automatically found conjectural relations between this and other sequences
xref: Essentially the same as A253560, except that here we have a(1) = 2.
results.author: _Antti Karttunen_, May 01 2007
